		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I don't agree that taking away control after you jump is ALWAYS a bad idea. Castlevania built the game around it. The trick is not so much to not do it, but to make your game work around it.<br /><br />Kinda like how people complain Banjo Kazooie is a collect-a-thon, but the game is built around it...why is that a bad thing?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


